Income from investments included in particular profit distributions from Siemens Ltd., China, amounting to €1,987 million, and from Siemens Healthineers AG, Germany, amounting to €634 million.

Income from profit transfer agreements with affiliated companies included profit transfers from Siemens Beteiligungen Inland GmbH, Germany, amounting to €1,323 million, and from Siemens Financial Services GmbH, Germany, amounting to €188 million.

Impairments on investments included an impairment of €164 million on a stake in Thoughtworks Holding, Inc., U.S.